description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-From Sannenzaka to Yasaka Pagoda
-Arashiyama in autumn leaves
-Kinkakuji Temple
-Osawa Pond in Spring
-Philosopher's Path in Autumn
-Okazaki Canal in Spring
-Hozukyo Gorge in autumn leaves
-Higashiyama at sunset
-Amanohashidate
-Bamboo forest in Sagano
name: Kyoto - Most beautiful places in Japan -
